#: ../../development/project-structure.md:1 36830bada2e64afb804c6b40450759b4
msgid "Project Structure"
msgstr "项目结构"

#: ../../development/project-structure.md:3 9b518c762701422a959a9e61b2c9af59
msgid ""
"This page describes the directory layout and module organization of "
"NotebookLM."
msgstr "本页介绍 NotebookLM 的目录布局和模块组织。"

#: ../../development/project-structure.md:5 0f470eed110549a991e32f9393b5919d
msgid "High-Level Structure"
msgstr "高层结构"

#: ../../development/project-structure.md:41 6ff59af6fc3a4735b8cbc0d1170b7d91
msgid "Directory Layout"
msgstr "目录布局"

#: ../../development/project-structure.md:119 2ad6453f1890405b8efb09b335fb9f3c
msgid "Key Modules"
msgstr "核心模块"

#: ../../development/project-structure.md:121 4fca0a753a0a47348d7a62177acd419d
msgid "App Router (`src/app/`)"
msgstr "App Router（`src/app/`）"

#: ../../development/project-structure.md:123 f9a43757cbae4a53854956faa6adcefe
msgid ""
"Next.js 16 App Router with file-based routing. Pages are server "
"components by default; client components use the `\"use client\"` "
"directive."
msgstr "Next.js 16 App Router，基于文件的路由。页面默认为服务器组件；客户端组件使用 `\\\"use client\\\"` 指令。"

#: ../../development/project-structure.md:125 aa7fa8323c594d7596ef2d7df3395a9a
msgid "Components (`src/components/`)"
msgstr "组件（`src/components/`）"

#: ../../development/project-structure.md:127 ce3a771e3033446fb6c609f5e51f6f8f
msgid ""
"React components organized by feature area. Uses shadcn/ui as the base "
"component library with Tailwind CSS for styling."
msgstr "按功能区域组织的 React 组件。使用 shadcn/ui 作为基础组件库，Tailwind CSS 进行样式设计。"

#: ../../development/project-structure.md:129 a4430f77396542c38aeb6b0cf5ef4cc7
msgid "Database (`src/lib/db/`)"
msgstr "数据库（`src/lib/db/`）"

#: ../../development/project-structure.md:131 e508fda57ad0463b8d7cdfcfd3f927f6
msgid ""
"SQLite database managed by Drizzle ORM. The schema defines tables for "
"workspaces, sources, source chunks, chunk embeddings, chat messages, "
"notes, settings, and skills."
msgstr ""
"由 Drizzle ORM 管理的 SQLite 数据库。Schema "
"定义了工作空间、来源、来源分块、分块嵌入、对话消息、笔记、设置和技能的表。"

#: ../../development/project-structure.md:133 06c5a78c1a424d0d8ea662b7057a3d4e
msgid "RAG Pipeline (`src/lib/rag/`)"
msgstr "RAG 流水线（`src/lib/rag/`）"

#: ../../development/project-structure.md:135 c7ed1cdda6aa4ccf98020c6e0f010056
msgid ""
"The Retrieval-Augmented Generation pipeline handles text chunking, vector"
" embedding, storage, and similarity search. Uses pure JavaScript cosine "
"similarity — no external vector database needed."
msgstr "检索增强生成流水线处理文本分块、向量嵌入、存储和相似性搜索。使用纯 JavaScript 余弦相似度 —— 无需外部向量数据库。"

#: ../../development/project-structure.md:137 c04b81db511e47dd926713edc6774f0b
msgid "Bot Integrations (`src/lib/bot/`)"
msgstr "机器人集成（`src/lib/bot/`）"

#: ../../development/project-structure.md:139 d1fca2465fad41639daa263eaff0074c
msgid ""
"Implements the `BotAdapter` interface for Feishu (Lark) and WeChat "
"Enterprise. Each adapter handles webhook verification, message parsing, "
"and response formatting."
msgstr "为飞书和企业微信实现了 `BotAdapter` 接口。每个适配器处理 Webhook 验证、消息解析和响应格式化。"
